src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e16b891400d60823c0a78cdbb12597884259ab84","tid":2049524,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1974f587d65b80ee979202e888d8d799647ab7d5","tid":2049524,"uid":147721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T13:54:02.000Z","msg":"鄰國公民無遮 無豬嘴 無頭盔 無瑜加帶 無国屍盾<br />\n佢地只係用肉身組成陣地 後排既堀磚碎磚 前排掟磚 再遠啲有人用車仔同貨車運更多大型磚石過黎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>此時距離罪犯開槍屠殺公民 尚餘大約十分鐘</strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T13:57:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a5b7a0a57349e6943d3cf71671202020525447","tid":2049524,"uid":147721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T14:04:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大約十點 鄰國配備裝甲車 號稱二十七軍既罪犯 係木犀地橋強行突破 同時有組織咁向公民掃射 展開屠殺</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n公民多人中彈倒下 其餘人邊跑走邊指控屠殺犯為「法西斯」「殺人犯」<br />\n佢地走入樓同樓中間既巷仔 同埋公園既樹叢<br />\n屠殺犯並無展開追捕 無開車撞埋去 而係直接向有口號既位置有組織地掃射<br />\n每處以十以百計既公民 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">倒於血泊中</span></strong>"},{"pid":"b902ca85ee0ab4eb80025eebb1d7f19b9c410a7d","tid":2049524,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T14:05:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f10e90e05fa4c71f1c765ed2048d01806e365383","tid":2049524,"uid":106472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T14:07:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da9f14a3bbeecf8723647c76ca09bb4aef53ec2","tid":2049524,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T14:11:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e0aae528512a107a296e6e625db082e8269d823","tid":2049524,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T14:17:47.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"52bc04abfb32a728b87d177c7f9289bed6f1746c","tid":2049524,"uid":312698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T14:20:46.000Z","msg":"毋忘64"},{"pid":"98ad99e5aa63e19ef9160e9ab3a4f7d6bea611fd","tid":2049524,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T14:43:56.000Z","msg":"大約十點半 木犀地既罪犯暫停推進<br />\n因為公民製造左着緊火既電車路障 武裝屠殺犯正在清理<br />\n製造呢啲路障既公民 一個鐘前佢地仲活生生係橋到同罪犯對峙 仲係黑夜中係催淚氣體中頂硬上 可能一邊流緊眼淚鼻涕 一邊掟緊石仔<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>此時武裝屠殺犯仍然係到掃射 附近矮樓食花生既支豚都有部分中槍身亡</strong></span>"},{"pid":"b7284c83a8d0a5adccfa11053e18e2bc70f49f81","tid":2049524,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T14:45:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c000077de414ae7479fae0dd0be65d90f1d0e63","tid":2049524,"uid":113187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T14:45:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"423a8270a86a1cfa1b92e9c820ca27c62ecea9ba","tid":2049524,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T14:54:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ab7e8a99d5ecfdb339e712a21191bc3ac93c78","tid":2049524,"ui